# Task Packets

When you start work, produce or request a Task Packet with:

- project_key: praxo-picos
- linear_issue_id, linear_session_id, run_id
- risk_tier: 0|1|2|3
- goal + acceptance criteria
- explicit scope boundaries
- required evaluations (tests, security scan, DQ, perf)
- gates required by tier
- outputs required (PR link, test commands, results)

Do not proceed without acceptance criteria.
